body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Car Dealership Support. My name is Donald Barnes. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Kimberly Henderson.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Kimberly. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling surprised to see incorrect data in my profile.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern. To assist you better, may I have your email address and phone number, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my email address is k.henderson@example.com and my phone number is five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Kimberly, for providing the information. I will look into this matter for you.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I appreciate your time today. Is there anything else I can assist you with?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Kimberly. Thank you for reaching out. Have a great day!
